-t%C6%B0-h%E1%BB%99-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-ZR08BeA5MDOJNc7zvtAUlg">Khốc Lưu tư hộ kỳ 1 - 哭劉司戶其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Xung-X%C3%A1c/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-ho%E1%BA%A1-ng%E1%BB%B1-ch%E1%BA%BF-H%E1%BA%A1nh-Ki%E1%BA%BFn-Thu%E1%BB%B5-%C4%91%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/poem-jEd-kGgqIkOwAARI7Nm_QA">Phụng hoạ ngự chế “Hạnh Kiến Thuỵ đường” - 奉和御製幸建瑞堂</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Xung-X%C3%A1c/author-apL4dZEfQkzDx1inl6wVQw">Nguyễn Xung Xác</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/S%C6%A1n-trung-k%C3%BD-ch%C6%B0-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-mu%E1%BB%99i/poem-vlXl7SIf0cKRMauCckmQRQ">Sơn trung ký chư đệ muội - 山中寄諸弟妹</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/author-9f1Hth0gmM_PXzGNXg5Fog">Vương Duy</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Phi/Thi%E1%BB%87n-tai-h%C3%A0nh-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-daIq9cfHi_hGWVIYxePORw">Thiện tai hành kỳ 1 - 善哉行其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Phi/author-_plJ3nwj8cVN02KPZ4P_8g">Tào Phi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/T%E1%BB%91ng-th%E1%BA%A5t-huynh-ph%C3%B3-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ch%C3%A2u-so%C3%A1i-m%E1%BA%A1c/poem-3zymIXZEHMiSBXKw9ewVOA">Tống thất huynh phó Dương Châu soái mạc - 送七兄赴揚州帥幕</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/author-6xOAUbKdWiBr-eAAn9zXQQ">Lục Du</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
